      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, peel and finely chop (or grate) the garlic</p>\r\n<p><strong>Reduce</strong> the heat to low, add the garlic, cumin seeds and cinnamon to the softened onions, then cook for a further 20 min or until caramelised</p>",
